name: A Voz da Fera
description:
I made this song specially for the Fam Jam Benefit Flash Auction that happened day 08/10/2021, where all the proceeds will be donated to our beloved friend Voces.
 This song is a homage to all our ancestors, that went through all challenges and burdens that life can provide, and even then left to the world their profound mark that is us.
The photo from the cover was took by me, through the window of my room.
